WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 33=

01:44.260 --> 01:48.260
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

02:10.300 --> 02:11.140
You're awake.

02:15.270 --> 02:16.110
Leave me.

02:26.550 --> 02:27.700
After all your scheming,

02:29.860 --> 02:31.580
seeing me like this,

02:32.900 --> 02:34.510
you must be quite pleased.

02:35.270 --> 02:36.110
How could that be?

02:37.140 --> 02:38.670
I'm only worried about you.

02:40.230 --> 02:41.270
After the punishment,

02:41.570 --> 02:42.790
you lost half your spirit power

02:42.801 --> 02:43.630
and fell unconscious.

02:44.420 --> 02:46.950
I cared for you the whole time.

02:50.140 --> 02:51.140
I'm not so weak

02:51.140 --> 02:52.270
as to need anyone's care.

02:56.510 --> 02:58.180
When I opened the wilds in North Abyss,

02:58.950 --> 03:00.230
evil spirits often attacked.

03:00.580 --> 03:01.862
To protect those spirit soldiers

03:01.873 --> 03:02.620
breaking the land,

03:02.950 --> 03:04.950
I devised a secret Zone.

03:05.860 --> 03:07.390
Your spirit power is weak now.

03:07.990 --> 03:09.070
So, I placed this Zone

03:09.350 --> 03:10.990
around this bedchamber

03:10.990 --> 03:11.950
to keep you safe.

03:12.860 --> 03:13.700
Simu,

03:14.020 --> 03:15.620
don't you love your rest days most?

03:16.350 --> 03:17.860
This is the perfect chance

03:18.230 --> 03:19.460
for you to rest well.

03:40.950 --> 03:42.460
With your spirit power as it is,

03:43.070 --> 03:44.550
you can't leave this bedchamber.

03:45.460 --> 03:46.700
What do you want?

03:48.350 --> 03:49.420
What do I want?

03:49.860 --> 03:51.350
Haven't you always known?

03:56.270 --> 03:57.700
Everything I've done

03:57.700 --> 03:58.620
was for you.

03:59.270 --> 04:01.390
I've even become

04:02.350 --> 04:03.740
like this because of you.

04:05.460 --> 04:06.700
Don't use me as your excuse.

04:10.020 --> 04:11.420
Do you still recall the moment

04:11.420 --> 04:12.670
I gave you my vital gate?

04:14.180 --> 04:15.580
Back then, I once thought

04:16.260 --> 04:17.500
that if you said yes,

04:18.030 --> 04:19.790
I would vow to serve you forever.

04:20.820 --> 04:21.670
But my true heart

04:21.670 --> 04:23.180
was cast aside like worn shoes.

04:29.940 --> 04:31.030
Luckily, now,

04:31.300 --> 04:33.060
everything can begin anew.

04:34.860 --> 04:35.990
From now on,

04:36.590 --> 04:37.552
everything here belongs

04:37.563 --> 04:38.550
only to the two of us.

04:39.860 --> 04:41.150
No matter what happens,

04:42.300 --> 04:44.350
I will always stay by your side.

04:55.790 --> 04:57.500
We have all the time we need.

04:58.110 --> 04:58.990
I will wait

04:59.740 --> 05:01.470
until the day you love me.

05:02.910 --> 05:03.990
Simu, I know

05:04.350 --> 05:05.230
you never wanted

05:05.230 --> 05:06.230
to be the Sovereign.

05:06.940 --> 05:08.030
I can help you.

05:09.110 --> 05:10.230
I will be the Sovereign.

05:10.990 --> 05:12.110
You'll be my Queen.

05:12.670 --> 05:14.150
Let us share the Void.

05:15.420 --> 05:17.470
I know what you need is company.

05:19.380 --> 05:21.060
I can spend all eternity

05:21.060 --> 05:21.900
by your side.

05:23.550 --> 05:24.390
We are

05:25.300 --> 05:27.380
a match made in heaven.

05:35.300 --> 05:36.260
As I told you,

05:37.350 --> 05:38.790
I will never hand the Void

05:38.790 --> 05:40.180
to someone I can't stand.

05:44.180 --> 05:45.470
The former Sovereign shaped you

05:45.470 --> 05:46.380
too deeply.

05:46.940 --> 05:47.860
I don't blame you.

05:56.860 --> 05:59.110
His laws have bound you fast.

05:59.710 --> 06:01.380
All you do is favor mortals.

06:02.420 --> 06:04.150
You even punished yourself.

06:05.420 --> 06:07.260
What is so great about mortals?

06:07.420 --> 06:08.820
They are small and fragile;

06:09.420 --> 06:10.940
their lives are fleeting.

06:17.110 --> 06:19.150
Spirits stand

06:19.740 --> 06:21.420
above all beings.

06:38.670 --> 06:39.510
Simu,

06:40.500 --> 06:42.500
from now on, your world has only me.

06:44.150 --> 06:45.550
Every day, I'll bring you

06:45.550 --> 06:46.710
some amusing little things.

06:47.380 --> 06:48.470
Wait for my return.

06:53.550 --> 06:54.390
And one more thing.

06:54.740 --> 06:55.790
I must remind you.

06:56.860 --> 06:58.590
Don't try to restore your spirit power.

06:59.300 --> 07:00.790
Under this restriction,

07:01.030 --> 07:03.470
your spirit power stays at its lowest.

07:04.230 --> 07:05.470
No matter how much you recover,

07:05.740 --> 07:07.300
this formation will drain it away.

07:08.740 --> 07:09.860
And this formation

07:10.350 --> 07:11.860
will only grow stronger.

07:46.300 --> 07:47.940
Your Lordship, you're finally here.

07:47.940 --> 07:49.030
Everyone's been waiting.

07:56.670 --> 07:57.990
Since everyone is here,

07:58.350 --> 07:59.910
let the morning assembly begin.

08:03.110 --> 08:04.150
Now that you oversee

08:04.150 --> 08:05.910
all affairs of the Void.

08:06.590 --> 08:08.420
I have questions

08:08.620 --> 08:09.670
about the spirit stones.

08:10.180 --> 08:11.020
You do?

08:11.990 --> 08:12.940
Let me hear it.

08:16.110 --> 08:17.820
This concerns the expenses you reported

08:17.820 --> 08:19.670
to Her Grace
about a North Abyss project.

08:20.060 --> 08:22.060
After making inquiries, we found

08:22.420 --> 08:23.375
the income and outgoings

08:23.386 --> 08:24.740
vastly differ

08:24.940 --> 08:26.260
from the reported accounts.

08:27.060 --> 08:27.900
I found as well

08:28.420 --> 08:29.260
that in recent years,

08:29.260 --> 08:30.790
when you were in charge,

08:31.180 --> 08:32.860
large sums went missing.

08:33.430 --> 08:34.270
Afterward,

08:34.430 --> 08:36.260
the same amount

08:36.540 --> 08:38.430
was moved into your private name.

08:40.950 --> 08:42.900
Someone is setting me up.

08:44.710 --> 08:45.900
Many have submitted reports.

08:46.230 --> 08:47.780
There must be more to this.

08:49.900 --> 08:51.830
I have reported this to Her Grace.

08:52.350 --> 08:53.500
Her Grace decreed

08:54.470 --> 08:55.950
to remove Jiang Ai

08:55.950 --> 08:57.660
from overseeing the Void affairs

08:57.900 --> 08:59.780
and to investigate her corruption.

09:00.830 --> 09:01.670
Also,

09:03.067 --> 09:04.913
Her Grace will enter seclusion
for five years.

09:05.380 --> 09:06.500
From this day forth,

09:07.540 --> 09:09.660
I shall assume full authority
over the Void.

09:11.710 --> 09:13.950
Why would Her Grace
enter seclusion for five years?

09:15.710 --> 09:16.550
Guards!

09:16.710 --> 09:17.780
Seize the Left Hand.

09:18.230 --> 09:19.070
Yes!

09:27.540 --> 09:29.070
I am the Void's Left Hand.

09:29.540 --> 09:30.710
Without Her Grace's order,

09:31.110 --> 09:32.430
who dares lay a hand on me?

09:33.620 --> 09:34.900
Jiang Ai,

09:36.070 --> 09:37.020
are you defying

09:37.020 --> 09:38.310
Her Grace's oral decree?

09:40.020 --> 09:41.540
Her Grace declared in public

09:41.540 --> 09:43.860
that I'd govern the Void for her.

09:44.500 --> 09:47.430
Everyone here heard it.

09:48.020 --> 09:49.230
Where did your oral decree

09:49.540 --> 09:50.740
come from?

09:51.230 --> 09:52.500
Who can vouch for it?

09:57.430 --> 09:58.470
Her Grace

09:58.900 --> 10:00.380
told me so herself.

10:08.660 --> 10:09.950
I'm the Left Hand.

10:10.710 --> 10:11.550
If I'm to be seized

10:11.900 --> 10:12.740
or investigated,

10:13.110 --> 10:14.740
Her Grace must give a clear order.

10:47.950 --> 10:48.900
Her Grace has ordered

10:48.900 --> 10:50.590
that none may disturb her in seclusion.

10:51.590 --> 10:52.590
Is that Her Grace's order

10:52.590 --> 10:53.620
or the Right Hand's order?

11:11.190 --> 11:12.030
Yan Ke,

11:12.500 --> 11:13.950
you've gone this far.

11:17.740 --> 11:19.350
You want to seize the Void,

11:19.540 --> 11:20.740
but it won't come so easily.

12:40.190 --> 12:41.030
Simu,

12:41.260 --> 12:42.740
haven't I told you before?

12:43.500 --> 12:45.046
Don't try to restore your spirit power.

12:46.140 --> 12:47.310
Why are you so disobedient?

12:48.620 --> 12:49.780
Why not lie down

12:49.780 --> 12:50.620
and have some rest?

12:52.710 --> 12:53.550
I'm fine.

12:57.350 --> 12:58.190
Simu,

12:59.310 --> 13:01.710
I gathered these kites from the Mortal World.

13:02.190 --> 13:03.310
Each one is ingenious.

13:04.110 --> 13:04.950
Do you like them?

13:06.540 --> 13:07.710
I had the string

13:08.140 --> 13:09.470
specially made.

13:10.110 --> 13:11.620
It's made of gold silkworm thread.

13:11.900 --> 13:12.740
Strong and durable.

13:13.190 --> 13:14.110
It won't snap.

13:17.230 --> 13:18.620
When I look at these kites,

13:18.620 --> 13:20.070
I find them most pleasing.

13:21.740 --> 13:23.590
A kite is held fast by its string,

13:24.140 --> 13:25.710
so it can never truly

13:25.990 --> 13:26.990
get away.

13:27.860 --> 13:28.700
Isn't that nice?

13:30.110 --> 13:31.430
Only with ties can you

13:32.140 --> 13:33.380
have a place to return to.

13:36.590 --> 13:38.380
From now on, I'll be your tie

13:38.830 --> 13:39.950
and your place to return to.

13:55.500 --> 13:56.500
Do you find this amusing?

13:57.110 --> 13:57.950
Of course.

13:58.190 --> 13:59.500
As long as I see you every day,

13:59.900 --> 14:01.140
it all feels amusing to me.

14:03.430 --> 14:04.830
Don't you like the Mortal World?

14:06.990 --> 14:07.900
Every day,

14:08.110 --> 14:09.860
I'll bring you something new.

14:10.660 --> 14:11.500
Soon,

14:12.429 --> 14:13.403
this place will be filled

14:13.414 --> 14:14.953
with memories that belong to us alone.

14:15.900 --> 14:16.740
Simu,

14:17.260 --> 14:18.190
do you still remember?

14:19.740 --> 14:21.500
After you became the Sovereign,

14:22.500 --> 14:23.470
I personally built

14:23.470 --> 14:24.740
this bedchamber for us.

14:29.430 --> 14:30.950
Lamps lit in the night sky,

14:33.430 --> 14:34.950
beneath the full moon high above,

14:36.380 --> 14:38.070
this is our home,

14:41.990 --> 14:43.900
just as its name promises,

14:45.230 --> 14:46.500
Zhaomu Pavilion.

14:47.430 --> 14:48.620
We'll always be together

14:49.430 --> 14:50.710
and never be parted.

14:52.900 --> 14:54.260
We are no longer ruler and subject,

14:54.260 --> 14:55.380
nor are we merely friends.

14:56.990 --> 14:58.710
We are each other's only

15:01.070 --> 15:02.310
and forever companions.

15:14.830 --> 15:16.140
Don't even dream about it.

15:52.140 --> 15:54.310
Whether it's a dream
or a desperate plea,

15:54.860 --> 15:56.620
don't you ever think of leaving my side.

15:57.860 --> 15:59.540
I have exhausted every possible way

15:59.540 --> 16:00.380
to love you.

16:00.660 --> 16:02.350
I have even offered you my heart,

16:02.500 --> 16:03.660
yet you refuse it utterly.

16:05.950 --> 16:07.350
Then I'd rather you hate me

16:08.110 --> 16:08.950
and blame me

16:10.110 --> 16:11.950
than neglect me.

16:25.190 --> 16:26.590
Since the things I gave you before

16:26.590 --> 16:27.860
were never to your liking,

16:31.310 --> 16:33.260
I will find you something else.

16:42.310 --> 16:43.590
Once you become the Sovereign,

16:45.140 --> 16:47.020
what will you make of the Void?

16:51.110 --> 16:53.350
Spirits are born of obsession.

16:53.350 --> 16:55.500
They should be free.

16:57.310 --> 16:58.470
Why should they be bound

16:58.470 --> 17:00.230
by all those rules and limits?

17:06.390 --> 17:08.060
In the Void that I rule,

17:08.470 --> 17:10.580
spirits should live as they please.

17:11.670 --> 17:13.430
What does that even mean?

17:14.150 --> 17:16.870
The strong endure and follow desire.

17:17.470 --> 17:19.780
First, the curfew must be abolished.

17:21.430 --> 17:22.340
Oh, right.

17:22.340 --> 17:23.230
I forgot to tell you.

17:24.250 --> 17:25.100
Your Left Hand

17:25.100 --> 17:26.670
is already all alone.

17:27.060 --> 17:28.870
No one obeys her anymore.

17:32.780 --> 17:34.500
Don't gloat just yet.

17:35.500 --> 17:36.430
If you could get

17:36.430 --> 17:37.630
what you want so easily,

17:38.260 --> 17:39.710
she would not be Jiang Ai.

17:52.580 --> 17:54.150
Simu,

17:55.300 --> 17:57.020
at a time like this,

17:58.390 --> 18:00.100
stop putting on a brave front.

18:04.340 --> 18:05.710
The time has come.

18:06.430 --> 18:08.300
I should go clean up the mess.

18:09.710 --> 18:10.780
Wait for my return.

18:35.100 --> 18:36.580
The stronger one lives.

18:37.060 --> 18:39.500
That is how spirits should be.

18:39.560 --> 18:40.430
That's right.

18:40.430 --> 18:42.670
The Right Hand should be Sovereign.

18:42.670 --> 18:43.950
The Golden-wall Decrees

18:43.950 --> 18:45.260
should be destroyed asap.

18:51.580 --> 18:52.540
How did this happen?

18:53.100 --> 18:54.580
The Void is in chaos.

19:00.870 --> 19:01.710
My Lord,

19:01.870 --> 19:02.950
the Xuling Temple is empty.

19:03.230 --> 19:04.070
There's nothing left.

19:07.390 --> 19:08.820
Jiang Ai, that sly old fox.

19:11.820 --> 19:13.540
Send more men across all of the Void.

19:14.260 --> 19:15.670
We must bring her back.

19:16.020 --> 19:16.860
- Yes.
- Yes.

19:42.150 --> 19:43.150
Bai Sanxing,

19:44.230 --> 19:45.300
it really is you.

19:53.910 --> 19:54.950
I'll kill you.

19:56.100 --> 19:57.300
I'm going to kill you.

20:35.420 --> 20:39.040
♪In silence, I gaze at you♪

20:39.240 --> 20:42.970
♪My hand hangs and then falls♪

20:43.320 --> 20:46.880
♪Let what stays unsaid pass♪

20:47.720 --> 20:51.130
♪Why torture each other like this?♪

20:51.410 --> 20:54.680
♪My wish might be♪

20:54.900 --> 20:58.280
♪Scattering like ripples♪

20:58.590 --> 21:04.670
♪With a gust of wind,
they fade like a dream♪

21:06.440 --> 21:10.300
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

21:10.300 --> 21:14.280
♪Fine rain falls dim and deep♪

21:14.280 --> 21:17.600
♪For the rest of my life♪

21:17.600 --> 21:21.660
♪I can hardly meet you again♪

21:21.830 --> 21:22.670
Bai Sanxing,

21:22.670 --> 21:23.540
once I have a chance,

21:23.540 --> 21:24.470
I'll make sure you die.

21:26.540 --> 21:27.380
Fine.

21:27.870 --> 21:28.710
I'll be waiting.

21:29.240 --> 21:34.850
♪Collapse piece by piece♪

21:37.370 --> 21:41.180
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

21:41.420 --> 21:44.980
♪And did not dare draw near again♪

21:45.210 --> 21:47.850
♪Leaving all behind♪

21:48.160 --> 21:52.780
♪The sudden pause of words unsaid♪

21:52.970 --> 21:56.600
♪How I long to hold that silhouette close♪

21:59.060 --> 21:59.900
Jiang Ai,

22:01.540 --> 22:02.430
it's you.

22:02.660 --> 22:09.450
♪All that is unfinished fade away♪

22:21.820 --> 22:23.060
Wasn't I in the Prison?

22:23.790 --> 22:26.760
♪In the end, love is the hardest to resist♪

22:26.780 --> 22:27.870
You let me out?

22:27.870 --> 22:31.300
♪Let memories drift and scatter♪

22:31.690 --> 22:34.560
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

22:36.340 --> 22:37.630
Her Grace spared your life.

22:38.230 --> 22:39.100
Take care of yourself.

22:39.450 --> 22:43.120
♪Till the past falls still again♪

22:43.240 --> 22:46.870
♪And turns to clear daylight♪

22:50.060 --> 22:54.380
(Shuozhou)

22:54.390 --> 22:55.230
Han,

22:55.820 --> 22:57.230
you were only framed

22:57.230 --> 22:58.300
by Chong spies.

22:58.950 --> 23:00.100
I'll avenge you.

23:01.230 --> 23:02.630
But why must you leave now?

23:02.630 --> 23:03.630
Shengliu, don't talk

23:04.300 --> 23:05.540
like it's a last farewell.

23:10.780 --> 23:11.780
We'll meet again.

23:13.780 --> 23:14.620
Commandant Wu,

23:15.020 --> 23:15.860
forgive me.

23:16.630 --> 23:17.740
I have my reasons.

23:20.950 --> 23:21.790
Captain Han,

23:24.230 --> 23:25.300
we'll meet again.

24:00.950 --> 24:01.870
Why did you save me?

24:05.340 --> 24:06.180
I wasn't saving you.

24:07.340 --> 24:08.180
I saved myself.

24:10.230 --> 24:11.540
It was that one belief

24:11.540 --> 24:12.380
that kept me going.

24:21.150 --> 24:22.740
I've been through

24:24.390 --> 24:25.449
what you're torn over now.

24:27.910 --> 24:28.820
From that day on,

24:31.670 --> 24:32.870
I was loyal only to myself.

24:37.670 --> 24:38.580
But you're different.

24:39.190 --> 24:40.950
Because of my selfish desire,

24:43.260 --> 24:44.470
I ignored your wishes

24:46.910 --> 24:48.390
and made that choice for you.

24:50.540 --> 24:51.780
For my arrogance,

24:53.190 --> 24:54.630
and for the scar on your face

24:56.020 --> 24:56.870
I owe you an apology.

24:59.500 --> 25:00.340
I'm sorry.

25:04.470 --> 25:05.310
You saved my life

25:07.340 --> 25:08.260
and apologized to me.

25:12.060 --> 25:12.990
I'm not so ungrateful

25:14.150 --> 25:15.190
as to miss your kindness.

25:19.910 --> 25:20.750
General.

25:29.540 --> 25:30.900
You're no longer who you once were.

25:34.020 --> 25:34.860
You should go.

25:37.150 --> 25:37.990
There are many things

25:39.927 --> 25:41.187
you need time to think through.

25:43.636 --> 25:44.922
You still have a long life ahead.

25:47.630 --> 25:48.470
Don't be afraid.

26:23.220 --> 26:25.300
(Liang)

26:25.300 --> 26:26.710
(Jingzhou)
(Duan Xu played along)

26:26.910 --> 26:29.060
(and took back Jingzhou from Chong forces.)

26:29.820 --> 26:30.710
(Later,)

26:30.710 --> 26:32.300
(the Fenglai Force attacked again.)

26:32.780 --> 26:35.100
(Duan Xu pressed on to Qizhou)

26:35.300 --> 26:36.540
(and killed the lead general.)

26:37.580 --> 26:39.153
(Qizhou)
(Chong forces fled in defeat.)

26:39.540 --> 26:41.500
(Duan Xu seized Qizhou in one stroke)

26:41.870 --> 26:44.470
(and was titled Marquis of Ningyi.)

26:55.780 --> 26:56.620
Let me do it.

26:58.300 --> 26:59.140
Yes.

27:15.540 --> 27:16.380
Xu,

27:17.150 --> 27:18.260
what's wrong with you?

27:18.990 --> 27:20.430
You fought like mad.

27:21.020 --> 27:22.190
What are you rushing for?

27:23.500 --> 27:24.780
It doesn't hurt that much.

27:27.540 --> 27:28.380
But Xu,

27:28.630 --> 27:30.430
you've lost a lot of blood.

27:31.100 --> 27:32.100
If Xiaoxiao finds out,

27:32.100 --> 27:33.020
she'll be worried.

27:43.060 --> 27:43.900
I understand.

27:44.430 --> 27:46.100
The General is eager to retake our land,

27:48.300 --> 27:49.733
but there's no need to push so hard.

27:50.430 --> 27:51.270
There is still time.

27:56.020 --> 27:57.190
Xu, but...

27:59.780 --> 28:00.706
General, get some rest.

28:01.260 --> 28:02.100
We'll take our leave.

28:04.100 --> 28:04.940
Come on.

28:09.190 --> 28:10.030
Chenying.

28:10.230 --> 28:11.070
Let's go.

28:14.870 --> 28:15.710
Come on.

28:16.580 --> 28:17.430
Move.

28:17.430 --> 28:18.270
Xu.

28:18.820 --> 28:19.660
Let's go.

28:24.630 --> 28:25.470
Simu.

28:29.470 --> 28:30.630
I called you.

28:34.950 --> 28:35.990
Why didn't you appear?

29:15.410 --> 29:16.479
Today, I made tea pastries

29:16.490 --> 29:17.670
from the Mortal World for you.

29:18.430 --> 29:19.270
Come.

29:22.470 --> 29:23.310
Have a taste.

29:23.990 --> 29:24.830
See if you like them.

29:35.630 --> 29:36.470
Simu,

29:37.630 --> 29:39.150
if only you'd yield a little.

29:39.500 --> 29:41.150
Even if it were a lie, I'd accept it.

29:42.580 --> 29:44.500
Why must you be so cold to me?

29:45.300 --> 29:47.260
Why drive me to this?

29:51.990 --> 29:53.150
Do you think I don't know

29:53.150 --> 29:54.340
what it is you've hidden?

29:57.870 --> 29:59.150
You still can't let go

29:59.150 --> 29:59.990
of that mortal.

30:01.820 --> 30:02.670
Other than me,

30:03.020 --> 30:04.230
you can't think of anyone else.

30:32.340 --> 30:33.820
I dote on you and cherish you,

30:34.470 --> 30:36.540
not so your heart may dwell
upon another.

30:38.710 --> 30:40.540
In your heart, there can only be me.

30:41.710 --> 30:43.430
Everyone else must die.

31:02.470 --> 31:03.910
Wait for me here.

31:05.190 --> 31:06.820
I'll be back soon.

31:38.580 --> 31:40.100
(Why has the Spirit Aura drifted here?)

32:23.630 --> 32:24.470
Yan Ke,

32:27.100 --> 32:28.060
what do you want?

33:39.630 --> 33:40.470
Prophet Hejia.

33:47.630 --> 33:49.390
Starhaven sorcerers.

33:50.340 --> 33:51.710
How dare you, evil spirit,

33:52.470 --> 33:54.190
harm mortals in the Mortal World?

33:54.820 --> 33:56.630
The Starhaven Sect will not spare you.

34:37.790 --> 34:38.630
Prophet Hejia,

34:38.910 --> 34:39.750
are you okay?

34:42.620 --> 34:43.460
It was to scare him.

34:44.500 --> 34:45.340
I'm here with you.

34:45.660 --> 34:46.500
Don't be afraid.

34:48.870 --> 34:49.710
Prophet Hejia.

34:50.500 --> 34:51.340
Prophet Hejia!

34:52.140 --> 34:52.980
Prophet Hejia!

35:23.750 --> 35:24.590
Prophet Hejia,

35:26.750 --> 35:27.590
you're finally awake.

35:31.100 --> 35:31.940
Prophet Hejia,

35:32.310 --> 35:33.700
do you know where Simu is?

35:34.950 --> 35:35.790
I can't find her.

35:41.470 --> 35:43.310
The Void has been very busy lately.

35:43.750 --> 35:45.060
As the Sovereign,

35:45.310 --> 35:46.580
she's burdened with duties.

35:47.100 --> 35:48.660
Even I dare not disturb her.

35:48.830 --> 35:49.670
General Duan,

35:49.950 --> 35:50.790
no need to worry.

35:51.750 --> 35:53.140
Then why are you here?

35:53.790 --> 35:54.910
You even saved me.

36:00.700 --> 36:02.700
Great Ancestor came to me earlier.

36:03.100 --> 36:04.470
She told me to keep you safe.

36:04.470 --> 36:05.660
As soon as I got the order,

36:05.870 --> 36:07.950
I rushed here without delay.

36:07.950 --> 36:09.790
I even changed horses several times.

36:10.020 --> 36:11.390
The horses never stopped.

36:11.390 --> 36:12.230
I nearly lost my life

36:12.990 --> 36:14.500
on the road.

36:16.500 --> 36:17.340
Luckily,

36:18.310 --> 36:20.130
your life was saved.

36:20.910 --> 36:21.750
My life

36:22.140 --> 36:23.350
was spared too.

36:23.870 --> 36:24.710
But Prophet Hejia...

36:25.990 --> 36:27.140
Easy now.

36:27.910 --> 36:29.310
Great Ancestor is mighty.

36:29.750 --> 36:31.660
She must be tied up and unable

36:31.660 --> 36:32.500
to come out.

36:33.020 --> 36:33.860
Don't worry.

36:34.060 --> 36:35.580
I'll look after you from now on.

36:36.470 --> 36:38.060
I still want to know where Simu is.

36:38.060 --> 36:38.950
Time for his medicine.

36:40.180 --> 36:41.020
You should go.

36:49.750 --> 36:50.870
Thank you for today.

36:51.870 --> 36:52.710
Please get some rest.

37:11.790 --> 37:13.020
With your current conditions,

37:14.060 --> 37:15.620
you should be resting at home.

37:16.350 --> 37:17.990
Yet you insist on meddling in this.

37:23.220 --> 37:24.220
Great Ancestor's affair

37:24.660 --> 37:25.700
is no trivial matter.

37:26.430 --> 37:28.100
She rarely entrusts me with much,

37:28.660 --> 37:29.750
so no matter what,

37:30.270 --> 37:31.390
I must see it through.

37:32.910 --> 37:34.910
All things have their destined fate.

37:35.660 --> 37:36.620
If you force your hand,

37:36.990 --> 37:37.910
it may bring no good.

37:41.350 --> 37:42.790
Aren't you interfering as well?

37:51.180 --> 37:52.020
Take your medicine.

37:52.830 --> 37:54.270
Your medicine

37:55.540 --> 37:57.270
can't change my fate.

38:00.220 --> 38:01.106
Great Ancestor's Pearl

38:02.500 --> 38:04.620
gives no reply,

38:05.270 --> 38:06.790
and spirits still wreak harm

38:06.790 --> 38:07.830
in the Mortal World.

38:09.540 --> 38:11.470
Something grave must've happened
in the Void.

38:13.140 --> 38:14.660
This matches the star

38:14.790 --> 38:15.750
of the great calamity

38:16.060 --> 38:16.910
in the ancient texts.

38:17.620 --> 38:19.350
The Mortal World faces a great calamity.

38:20.470 --> 38:21.830
As the Lord of Starhaven Sect,

38:22.790 --> 38:24.390
it is my duty to save the world.

38:24.950 --> 38:26.390
I can't stand by and do nothing.

38:27.430 --> 38:28.270
Only by staying alive

38:29.060 --> 38:29.980
can you save the world.

38:47.950 --> 38:49.060
Help!

38:52.870 --> 38:54.020
The High Priest is here.

38:54.020 --> 38:56.220
- High Priest.
- High Priest.

38:56.220 --> 38:57.060
Please save us.

39:02.950 --> 39:04.270
Hold on.

39:09.060 --> 39:10.060
It doesn't hurt anymore.

39:11.100 --> 39:12.500
Thank you for your protection.

39:13.310 --> 39:15.220
Cangshen protects my people.

39:19.620 --> 39:20.700
My leg.

39:20.830 --> 39:21.750
- High Priest.
- Yes.

39:21.750 --> 39:23.876
- High Priest, save me.
- With the High Priest here,

39:23.887 --> 39:24.660
we're safe.

39:24.660 --> 39:25.500
Save me.

39:28.580 --> 39:29.430
Report!

39:30.100 --> 39:31.620
- Here.
- High Priest,

39:31.750 --> 39:32.719
the General invites you

39:32.730 --> 39:33.470
to the camp to plan

39:33.660 --> 39:34.990
how to strike the foe

39:35.073 --> 39:36.350
in the coming Battle of Weizhou.

39:40.260 --> 39:41.100
Hold on.

39:41.100 --> 39:41.940
Lead the way.

39:46.140 --> 39:48.820
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

40:00.620 --> 40:02.140
I went to kill Duan Xu.

40:05.790 --> 40:06.990
He had just come from battle,

40:07.470 --> 40:08.750
with his wounds unhealed.

40:11.020 --> 40:12.950
I struck him down so hard

40:14.220 --> 40:16.140
that he could only murmur your name.

40:18.020 --> 40:19.646
He was mentally and physically shattered.

40:20.430 --> 40:22.020
I doubt he has long to live.

40:26.220 --> 40:27.990
How does it feel to be cut

40:27.990 --> 40:29.020
by the Deliverance?

40:32.540 --> 40:33.540
Starhaven sorcerers

40:33.540 --> 40:34.750
were tough, right?

40:41.430 --> 40:43.060
As expected of you, Simu.

40:43.540 --> 40:45.500
You've arranged everything so well.

40:46.660 --> 40:48.060
You truly feared I'd kill him.

40:49.020 --> 40:50.540
You gave him an amulet

40:50.551 --> 40:52.129
and even had the Lord of Starhaven Sect

40:52.140 --> 40:52.910
protect him.

40:54.020 --> 40:55.750
A mortal as lowly as an ant

40:57.100 --> 40:59.470
can only cling to life under you.

40:59.660 --> 41:01.310
What is it you love about him?

41:03.700 --> 41:04.700
You said you loved me,

41:05.580 --> 41:06.660
yet you used such tricks

41:06.660 --> 41:07.660
to keep me trapped here.

41:08.870 --> 41:10.540
Even with my spirit power lost,

41:13.180 --> 41:15.060
you still can't do anything to me.

41:16.830 --> 41:17.670
Yan Ke,

41:19.060 --> 41:21.350
did you truly do all this for me?

41:23.020 --> 41:24.990
Have you forgotten what birthed you?

41:26.990 --> 41:28.390
You crave power and rank.

41:30.580 --> 41:31.790
You're only obsessed

41:32.140 --> 41:33.140
with power in your life.

41:34.100 --> 41:36.710
Your desires will never end.

41:39.310 --> 41:40.910
What you want is power,

41:42.540 --> 41:44.500
the highest power of all.

41:56.870 --> 41:58.270
Simu, you're wrong.

42:00.430 --> 42:01.540
What I've wanted

42:04.830 --> 42:06.500
has always been your heart.

42:15.180 --> 42:16.750
Our lives are long.

42:18.500 --> 42:19.990
I'll wait with you.

42:21.310 --> 42:22.500
I'll make you watch him

42:22.500 --> 42:23.830
fade away bit by bit.

42:25.270 --> 42:26.620
I'll wait for the day

42:28.430 --> 42:29.700
you finally forget him.

43:10.310 --> 43:11.310
Foxy,

43:22.700 --> 43:24.310
stay alive.

43:30.120 --> 43:35.450
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:35.780 --> 43:40.030
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:41.390 --> 43:46.760
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:47.060 --> 43:51.660
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:52.750 --> 43:54.590
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:06.800 --> 44:12.240
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:12.420 --> 44:16.750
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:18.120 --> 44:23.510
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:23.740 --> 44:27.680
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:29.450 --> 44:31.340
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:34.000 --> 44:37.160
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:37.160 --> 44:39.690
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:39.690 --> 44:45.210
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:45.210 --> 44:48.450
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:48.450 --> 44:53.310
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:53.650 --> 44:56.670
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:56.670 --> 44:59.490
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:59.750 --> 45:02.280
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

45:02.280 --> 45:07.700
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

45:07.870 --> 45:10.940
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

45:11.100 --> 45:16.000
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

45:16.210 --> 45:19.680
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
